text: Compsosoma chabrillacii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Thomson in 1857. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Compsosoma chabrillacii. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1857
